Class DateUtils

java.lang.Object
  wogwt.translatable.utils.DateUtils

public final class DateUtils
extends java.lang.Object

WOGWT: copied from gwt-restlet to be used to parse and format JSON dates in the format(s) required by ERRouteRequestHandler. Date manipulation utilities.
